7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"How does ISO 45001 Certification Benefit Manufacturing Companies?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:31:24+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"ISO 45001  certification in Dubai establishes a globally recognized set of criteria for developing an Occupational Health and Safety Management System that may"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How does ISO 45001 Certification Benefit Manufacturing Companies?"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"You may be contemplating the necessity for an Occupational Health & Safety Management System (OHSMS) for your business as a manufacturing firm, and ISO 45001:2015 is a standard that you should examine as the prerequisites for establishing the management system. Because several risks must be addressed, the manufacturing business has a crucial requirement for excellent occupational health and safety management. ISO 45001 certification in Dubai establishes a globally recognized set of criteria for developing an Occupational Health and Safety Management System that may be customized for your industrial business."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 14001 specifications for the manufacturing industry"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Safety management systems are no longer novel in the industrial business, as employee safety is critical to the ability to complete tasks. However, many security administration organizations are patched together to meet criminal requirements as they emerge. To improve the situation, the iso 45001 ohsms benefits for employees and has created a set of requirements in the ISO 45001 standard based on worldwide best practices for managing occupational health and safety (OHS) in the workplace."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"While ISO certification in UAE has an appendix with implementation guidelines, ISO has also produced supporting standards to aid in implementation and other aspects of occupational health; a short search on the ISO webpage yields 36 standards. The new ISO/DIS 45003 is being discussed for managing psychological health and safety at work, while the ISO/AWI 45002 provides further general principles for implementing ISO 45001. ISO/TS 24179:2020 for OH&S measurements for human resources and ISO/TS 20559:2020 for the creation and implementation of a safety signaling system are two other guideline publications. None of these extra standards are necessary for ISO 45001 to be implemented, However, you can use them as a reference for certain parts of OH&S management."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Implementing ISO 45001 Certification in Dubai manufacturing organizations"}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16"]}],"$L17"]}]}]
